trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.
The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection> is used to compile custom resource files.
You can have any number of build providers.
The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection> does not refer to any actual element in the underlying configuration file.
It is a construct that allows easy access to the compilation information it contains.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"></xref> class.
Adds a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> object to the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"></xref>.
If the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider> object already exists in the collection, the build provider is ignored.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> object.
Clears all <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> objects from the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"></xref>.
Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> object at the specified index of the collection.
An integer value specifying a particular <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> object within the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"></xref>.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> object.
Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> collection element based on the specified name.
The name of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> object to return from the collection.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> object.
Removes a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"></xref>.
If the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider> does not exist in the collection, the build provider is ignored.
A string value specifying the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> reference.
Removes the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> object at the specified index from the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"></xref>.
If the index does not specify a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider> in the collection, an out-of-range exception is thrown.

An integer value specifying the location of a specific <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProvider"></xref> object within the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"></xref>.
